{"tid":576594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頌安邨男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-03-01T04:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T04:42:21.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"28f274fa8596f02abb0a1c657ed1eaf521ea4930","tid":576594,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180301/large/1519878443_edc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180301%2Flarge%2F1519878443_edc7.jpg&h=b8af60c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子送院搶救不治。(劉柏麟攝)<br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山頌安邨頌智樓，上午11時，一名30餘歲男子由高處墮下，倒卧平台重傷昏迷，送院搶救後不治。警方正調查死者身份及墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180301/57890021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F57890021&d=yHZ6qo3DXskkgu8vni9lusn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=10a8c197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180301%2F57890021&h=b66dc91f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180301/57890021</a>"},{"pid":"bde7209cabb984fc85a981424fd5288864df877d","tid":576594,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"一定係驚DSE俾人玩"},{"pid":"a92fc4a535e198878a39685ccabe35d2e75f31f6","tid":576594,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T04:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a507a3fe856eb7478195925f9d28506c84b48c","tid":576594,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T04:42:21.000Z","msg":"無錢派<